<div style="margin-bottom:20px;">
  <div style="font-size:15px; font-weight:800; color:#92400e; margin-bottom:6px;">Transfè Ekspire</div>
  <div style="font-size:13px; color:#5D6345;">Transfè #<%= @transfer.id %> — <%= @transfer.updated_at.strftime("%b %d, %Y") %></div>
</div>

<div style="background:#fef3c7; border:2px solid #92400e; border-radius:14px; padding:16px; margin-bottom:16px;">
  <table width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
    <tr>
      <td style="color:#92400e; font-size:12px; font-weight:600; padding-bottom:8px;">Montan</td>
      <td style="color:#2E2E38; font-weight:800; text-align:right; padding-bottom:8px;">HTG <%= format('%.0f', @transfer.amount.to_f) %></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="color:#92400e; font-size:12px; font-weight:600;">Resevè</td>
      <td style="color:#2E2E38; font-weight:600; text-align:right;">
        <%= @transfer.receiver_name.presence || @transfer.receiver_phone.presence || @transfer.receiver_email.presence || "—" %>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</div>

<div style="font-size:13px; color:#5D6345; line-height:1.6;">
  Transfè sa a te ekspire paske moun nan pa t reklame lajan an nan delè a. N ap trete yon ranbousman nan kont ou.
</div>
